Electrical Conductivity</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div id=\"water-analysis\" class=\"content\">\r\n        <h2>Water Analysis</h2>\r\n        <h3>Anions (-)</h3>\r\n        <label for=\"chloride\">Chloride (Cl) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"chloride\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"phosphate\">Phosphate (HPO) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"phosphate\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"sulfite\">Sulfite (SO) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"sulfite\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"sulfate\">Sulfate (SO) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"sulfate\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"carbonate\">Carbonate (CO) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"carbonate\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"bicarbonate\">Bicarbonate (HCO) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"bicarbonate\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"fluoride\">Fluoride (F) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"fluoride\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"nitrite\">Nitrite (NO) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"nitrite\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"nitrate\">Nitrate (NO) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"nitrate\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"silicate\">Silicate (SiO) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"silicate\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <h3>Cations (+)</h3>\r\n        <label for=\"sodium\">Sodium (Na) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"sodium\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"calcium\">Calcium (Ca) (mgpL):</label>\r\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"calcium\" placeholder=\"Enter value\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"magne