INSERT INTO `faq` (`faq_id`, `product_id`, `faq_question`, `faq_answer`) VALUES
(1, 1, 'What is wax paper?', ' Wax paper is a type of paper coated with a thin layer of wax to make it moisture-resistant and non-stick.\n\nUse:\n\nWax paper is ideal for wrapping food items like sandwiches and baked goods to keep them fresh. Its also great for lining countertops when rolling out dough or for wrapping foods that need to stay moist.'),
(2, 0, 'What products do Deli Paper offer?', 'Deli Paper provides a diverse range of high-quality, eco friendly paper products, including parchment paper, butcher paper, wrapping paper, wax paper, and food wrapping paper. Each product is crafted to meet your everyday needs with elegance and practicality.'),
(3, 0, 'Where can I buy Deli Paper products?', ' You can explore and purchase our full range of products on our Deli Papers Official Site. For further inquiries, call us at +447366426960 or visit us at 72 Booker Lane, High Wycombe, HP12 3UT.\r\n\r\n'),
(4, 0, 'How do I contact customer service?', ' You can explore and purchase our full range of products on our Deli Papers Official Site. For further inquiries, call us at +447366426960 or visit us at 72 Booker Lane, High Wycombe, HP12 3UT.'),
(5, 0, 'Can I track my order once it has been placed?', 'Yes, you will receive a tracking number once your order has been dispatched, allowing you to monitor its progress until it arrives at your doorstep.\r\n\r\n'),
(6, 0, 'What if my order arrives damaged?', ' If your order arrives damaged, please contact our customer service team immediately so we can resolve the issue for you.'),
(7, 0, 'Do you offer international shipping?', 'Yes, we ship our products internationally. Shipping costs and delivery schedules will vary according to your location. \r\n\r\n'),
(8, 0, 'What is your return policy?', 'We offer a hassle free return policy on most of our products. If youre not satisfied with your purchase, please contact us within 30 days of receipt to arrange a return or exchange.'),
(9, 0, 'What makes Deli Papers wrapping paper special?', 'Our wrapping paper combines style and sustainability. Its made from eco friendly materials and features elegant designs perfect for any occasion, ensuring your gifts are beautifully presented.'),
(10, 1, 'Can I use wax paper in the oven?', 'No, wax paper should not be used in the oven as the wax can melt and potentially catch fire.'),
(11, 1, 'Is wax paper the same in use as parchment paper?', ' No, wax paper is coated with wax and is not heat-resistant, while parchment paper is coated with silicone and can withstand high temperatures.'),
(12, 1, 'Can I reuse wax paper?', 'Yes, if its not too soiled, wax paper can be wiped clean and reused.'),
(13, 1, 'Is wax paper eco-friendly?', 'Wax paper is biodegradable, but its always good to check if its made from sustainably sourced materials.'),
(14, 1, 'How do I store wax paper?', 'Store wax paper in a cool, dry place away from heat sources to prevent the wax from melting.\r\n\r\n'),
(15, 1, 'Whats the difference between wax paper and greaseproof paper?', 'Wax paper is coated with wax to make it moisture-resistant, while greaseproof paper is treated to resist grease and moisture but is not coated with wax.\r\n\r\n'),
(16, 1, 'How do I use wax paper to wrap food?', 'How do I use wax paper to wrap food?'),
(17, 1, 'What is wax paper used for?', 'Wax paper is ideal for wrapping food items like sandwiches and baked goods to keep them fresh. Its also great for lining countertops when rolling out dough or for wrapping foods that need to stay moist.\r\n\r\n'),
(18, 2, 'What is butcher paper?', 'Butcher paper is a type of thick, sturdy paper used primarily for wrapping meats. Its commonly found in butcher shops, delis, and kitchens due to its durability and ability to keep meats fresh.'),
(19, 2, 'How is butcher paper different from other types of paper?', 'Butcher Paper vs. Parchment Paper: \n\r\n\r\nParchment paper is covered with silicone, making it nonstick and heat-resistant, making it perfect for baking. Butcher paper is uncoated, which makes it more breathable and ideal for wrapping and preserving meat.\n \r\n\r\nButcher Paper vs. Wax Paper: \n\r\n\r\nWax paper is covered with wax, which makes it moisture-resistant and ideal for wrapping cold items. However, it is not ideal for hot temperatures. Butcher paper is more versatile, able to handle both wet and dry foods, and is suitable for low-heat cooking.\n\r\n\r\nButcher Paper vs. Greaseproof Paper: \n\r\n\r\nGreaseproof paper is intended to withstand grease and moisture, making it excellent for baking. Butcher paper is thicker and more robust, making it ideal for wrapping and storing meats. '),
(20, 2, 'Can butcher paper be used in the oven?', 'Yes, butcher paper can be used in the oven, particularly for smoking and low-temperature cooking. It allows the meat to breathe while keeping it moist and flavourful.\r\n\r\n'),
(21, 2, 'Is butcher paper food-safe?', ' Yes, Deli Papers butcher paper is food-grade, meaning its safe for wrapping meats and other food items. Its designed with high-quality materials to assure safety and durability.\r\n\r\n'),
(22, 2, 'Discover the Excellence of Deli Papers Butcher Paper?', 'Butcher paper from Deli Paper is more than simply a wrapping tool its a flexible companion that will elevate your cooking experience. It comes in handy rolls and sheets and fits well into your busy British kitchen.\r\n\r\n'),
(23, 2, 'Is butcher paper eco-friendly?', 'Yes, our butcher paper is made from sustainable materials, making it an eco-friendly choice. It is biodegradable and recyclable, which reduces environmental effect.'),
(24, 2, 'How do I use butcher paper for smoking meat?', 'To use butcher paper for smoking meat, simply wrap your meat in the paper after its been seasoned and partially cooked. This helps keep the meat moist and allows smoke to penetrate, enhancing the flavour.'),
(25, 2, 'Can I use butcher paper for wrapping gifts?', 'Absolutely. Butcher paper can be used creatively for gift wrapping. Its sturdy nature makes it perfect for creating personalised gift wrap, adding a rustic and charming touch to any present.\r\n\r\nAdd a roll to your cart today to experience the excellent quality and adaptability of Deli Papers butcher paper. Deli Paper provides a unique combination of functionality and elegance.'),
(26, 3, 'What is wrapping paper used for?', 'Wrapping paper is used to cover and decorate gifts, making them look special and exciting for the recipient. Its perfect for birthdays, holidays, and any occasion where you want to give a present.\r\n\r\n'),
(27, 3, 'Can wrapping paper be recycled?', 'Yes, most wrapping papers from Deli Paper are recyclable. Always check for any non-recyclable elements like glitter or metallic finishes and remove them before recycling.\r\n\r\n'),
(28, 3, 'Can I use wrapping paper for other projects?', ' Absolutely. Wrapping paper is great for scrapbooking, making personalised gift tags, and even lining drawers or covering books for a decorative touch.\r\n\r\n'),
(29, 3, 'What is wrapping paper?', 'Wrapping paper is decorative paper used to cover and decorate gifts, adding a special touch to presents.\r\n\r\n'),
(30, 3, 'Is wrapping paper suitable for all types of gifts?', 'Yes, wrapping paper is versatile and can be used for almost any type of gift. Its especially great for boxes, books, and similarly shaped items.\r\n\r\n'),
(31, 3, 'Discover the Excellence of Deli Papers Wrapping Paper?', 'Deli Papers wrapping paper is not just for wrapping gifts its a versatile, eco-friendly choice that adds a touch of elegance to any present. Add a roll to your cart today and see why our wrapping paper is the perfect choice for every occasion \r\n\r\n'),
(32, 3, 'Why choose Deli Paper`s wrapping paper?', 'Deli Papers wrapping paper is high-quality, durable, and available in stylish designs. Its eco-friendly and made from sustainable materials, ensuring your gifts look beautiful while being kind to the planet.'),
(33, 3, 'What sizes do Deli Paper`s wrapping papers come in?', ' Deli Paper offers wrapping paper in various sizes, from rolls to sheets, so you can choose the perfect amount for your needs. \r\n\r\n'),
(34, 3, 'What are the different designs available for Deli Paper`s wrapping paper?', 'Deli Paper offers a wide range of designs, from classic and elegant patterns to fun and festive prints. Every occasion and fashion desire can be satisfied.Every occasion and fashion desire can be satisfied.'),
(35, 4, 'What is gift wrapping paper?', 'Gift wrapping paper is decorative paper used to cover and decorate presents, adding a special touch to your gifts.\r\n\r\n'),
(36, 4, 'Why should I use Deli Paper`s gift wrapping paper?', 'Deli Papers gift wrapping paper is high-quality, stylish, and eco-friendly. Its designed to make your gifts look beautiful and thoughtful while being kind to the environment.\r\n\r\n'),
(37, 4, 'Can Deli Paper`s gift wrapping paper be recycled?', 'Yes, most of our gift wrapping paper is recyclable. Just make sure to remove any non-recyclable elements like glitter or metallic finishes.\r\n\r\n'),
(38, 4, 'What sizes are available for Deli Paper`s gift wrapping paper?', 'Our gift wrapping paper is available in various sizes, from rolls to sheets, so you can find the perfect amount for your needs.\r\n\r\n'),
(39, 4, 'Can I use gift wrapping paper for other projects?', 'Absolutely. Our wrapping paper is great for scrapbooking, making gift tags, lining drawers, and other creative DIY crafts.\r\n\r\n'),
(40, 4, 'What designs are available for Deli Paper`s gift wrapping paper?', 'Deli Paper offers a wide range of designs, from classic and elegant patterns to fun and festive prints, perfect for any occasion.\r\n\r\n'),
(41, 4, 'Is gift wrapping paper suitable for all types of gifts?', ' Yes, gift wrapping paper is versatile and can be used for almost any type of gift, especially boxes, books, and other similarly shaped items.\r\n\r\nAdd a roll to your cart today to experience the excellent quality and adaptability of Deli Papers butcher paper. Deli Paper provides a unique combination of functionality and elegance.'),
(42, 4, 'Discover the Beauty of Deli Papers Gift Wrapping Paper?', 'Deli Papers gift wrapping paper is not just for wrapping presents its a versatile, eco-friendly choice that adds a touch of elegance to any gift. Add a roll to your cart today and see why our wrapping paper is the perfect choice for every occasion.\r\n\r\n'),
(43, 5, 'What are Deli Paper`s paper bags made from?', 'Our paper bags are made from high-quality, food-grade materials that are safe for all your packaging needs. They are also eco-friendly, made from sustainable sources to ensure minimal environmental impact.\r\n\r\n'),
(44, 5, 'What sizes are available for Deli Paper`s paper bags?', 'Deli Paper offers a range of sizes to suit various needs, from small bags perfect for gift wrapping to larger bags ideal for grocery shopping and food packaging.\r\n\r\n'),
(45, 5, 'Can I use Deli Paper`s paper bags for food?', 'Absolutely. Our paper bags are food-grade, making them safe for packing sandwiches, baked goods, and other food items. They are also great for use as food wrapping paper, sandwich wrap paper, and parchment paper.\r\n\r\n'),
(46, 5, 'How do paper bags compare to fabric bags?', 'While fabric bags are more durable and reusable, paper bags are a great single-use option that is cost-effective and eco-friendly. Paper bags can also be recycled, whereas fabric bags require more resources to produce and maintain.\r\n\r\n'),
(47, 5, 'Can Deli Paper`s paper bags be reused?', 'Yes, our high-quality paper bags can be reused if kept in good condition. They are strong enough to handle multiple uses, making them a versatile choice for various applications.\r\n\r\n'),
(48, 5, 'What are some common uses for paper bags?', 'Deli Papers paper bags are incredibly versatile and can be used for:\r\n\r\nShopping: Ideal for carrying groceries and retail purchases.\r\n\r\nGift Wrapping: Perfect for creating personalised gift bags and wrapping gifts.\r\n\r\nFood Packaging: Great for bakeries and delis, keeping food items fresh and presentable.\r\n\r\nCreative Projects: Suitable for DIY projects and crafting personalised wrapping paper or unique gift wrap.'),
(49, 5, 'Discover the Excellence of Deli Papers Paper Bags?', ' Deli Papers paper bags are more than just packaging theyre versatile solutions that enhance your everyday life. Available in convenient packs, they fit seamlessly into your daily routines and special occasions.\r\n\r\n'),
(50, 5, 'How do Deli Paper`s paper bags contribute to sustainability?', ' By choosing Deli Papers paper bags, you are supporting eco-friendly packaging solutions. Our bags are made from sustainable materials, reducing the reliance on single-use plastics and helping to minimise environmental impact.\r\n\r\n'),
(51, 6, 'What is parchment paper?', 'Parchment paper is a non-stick, heat-resistant paper used in baking and cooking.'),
(52, 6, 'Can I use parchment paper for wrapping food?', 'Absolutely. Parchment paper is great for wrapping sandwiches, pastries, and other food items. It preserves food and prevents it from sticking.\r\n\r\n'),
(53, 6, 'Is parchment paper reusable?', ' Yes, high-quality parchment paper can be wiped clean and reused multiple times.\r\n\r\n'),
(54, 6, 'Can I wrap food with parchment paper?', 'Absolutely, parchment paper is perfect for wrapping food like sandwiches and pastries.\r\n\r\n'),
(55, 6, 'What is the difference between parchment paper and wax paper?', 'Wax paper is moisture-resistant but not heat-resistant, whereas parchment paper is both heat-resistant and non-stick, making it suitable for baking.\r\n\r\n'),
(56, 6, 'What can I use parchment paper for?', 'Parchment paper is great for baking, cooking, food wrapping, and even gift wrapping.\r\n\r\n'),
(57, 6, 'How is parchment paper different from greaseproof paper?', 'The parchment paper is coated with silicone, providing superior non-stick and heat-resistant properties. Greaseproof paper is treated to resist grease but does not have the same heat resistance as parchment paper.\r\n\r\n'),
(58, 6, 'Can I use parchment paper in the oven?', 'Yes, Deli Papers parchment paper is safe for oven use and can handle high temperatures.\r\n\r\n'),
(59, 6, 'How does parchment paper compare to wax paper?', 'Wax paper is coated with wax, making it moisture-resistant but not heat-resistant, so it cant be used in the oven. Parchment paper is both heat-resistant and nonstick, making it ideal for baking and cooking.\r\n\r\n'),
(60, 6, 'Discover the Excellence of Deli Papers Parchment Paper?', 'Deli Papers parchment paper is a versatile tool that enhances your cooking and baking experience. Add a roll to your cart today and enjoy the blend of practicality and elegance that only Deli Paper can offer.\r\n\r\n'),
(61, 7, 'What is greaseproof paper?', 'Greaseproof paper is a type of paper treated to resist grease and moisture, making it perfect for baking, cooking, and wrapping food.\r\n\r\n'),
(62, 7, 'Can I use greaseproof paper in the oven?', 'Yes, Deli Papers greaseproof paper is safe for oven use and can handle high temperatures.\r\n\r\n'),
(63, 7, 'Is greaseproof paper the same as parchment paper?', 'No, greaseproof paper is treated to resist grease but lacks the silicone coating that makes parchment paper non-stick and more heat-resistant.\r\n\r\n'),
(64, 7, 'What are the common uses of greaseproof paper?', 'Greaseproof paper is versatile and can be used for baking, cooking, wrapping food, and even gift wrapping.\r\n\r\n'),
(65, 7, 'Can greaseproof paper be reused?', ' Yes, high-quality greaseproof paper can be wiped clean and reused multiple times.\r\n\r\n'),
(66, 7, 'How does greaseproof paper compare to wax paper?', 'Greaseproof paper is heat-resistant and ideal for baking, while wax paper is moisture-resistant but not suitable for oven use.\r\n\r\n'),
(67, 7, 'How do I use greaseproof paper for baking?', 'Line your baking tray or cake tin with greaseproof paper to prevent sticking and ensure easy removal of your baked goods.\r\n\r\n'),
(68, 7, 'Can greaseproof paper be used to wrap food?', 'Absolutely. Greaseproof paper is great for wrapping sandwiches, pastries, and other food items to keep them fresh.\r\n\r\n'),
(69, 7, 'Why choose Deli Papers greaseproof paper?', ' Deli Papers greaseproof paper is high-quality, durable, and eco-friendly, making it a perfect choice for all your baking and cooking needs.\r\n\r\n'),
(70, 7, 'How does greaseproof paper compare to wax paper?', 'Greaseproof paper is heat-resistant and ideal for baking, while wax paper is moisture-resistant but not suitable for oven use.\r\n\r\n');

