><p>Our paper is easy to cut, fold, and tape, providing a hassle-free wrapping experience.</p><p><strong>Why should everyone use Deli Papers gift wrap paper?</strong></p><p>Deli Paper recognises the significance of presentation when it comes to gift-giving. Our gift wrapping paper is intended to make your gifts stand out and show your loved ones how much you care. Whether youre wrapping a modest token or a large gift, our paper provides that particular touch.</p><p>Our gifts wrapping material is both useful and creative. Use it to create personalised wrapping paper, birthday wrapping paper, or present wrapping paper. Its adaptability makes it ideal for making gift bags, wrapping paper, and other products. The luxury look and feel elevate any gift.</p><p>Discover the beauty and versatility of Deli Papers gift wrapping paper. Available in rolls and sheets, it fits seamlessly into your gift-giving routine, making every present memorable and elegant.</p><p>Add a roll to your cart today and see why Deli Papers gift wrapping paper is the perfect choice for every occasion.</p>', '1745257707_8055_Custom Printed paper (1000 x 1000 ).jpg', '', '', 'Elegant Gift Wrapping Paper, Perfect for Every Occasion', 'Discover our collection of exquisite gift wrapping papers, designed to add a touch of elegance to your presents. Eco-friendly materials and stylish designs .', '', 'active', '2025-04-21 16:50:49', '2025-05-07 05:23:15', 'yes'),
(5, 'Paper Bags', 'paper-bags', 'There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but the majority have suffered alteration in some form, by injected humour.There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but the majority have suffered alteration in some form, by injected humour. Our paper is food-safe, vegan-friendly, and Halal-certified. We offer extensive customization options, a free design service and free shipping. Versatile for any kitchen, our paper is microwavable, ovenproof, and freezeproof, suitable for both hot and cold food.Embrace sustainability with our eco-friendly paper bags, designed to meet your everyday packaging needs while reducing environmental impact. Crafted from responsibly sourced materials, these paper bags offer a perfect blend of durability, functionality, and eco-consciousness.', '<ol><li><strong>Environmentally Responsible Production</strong></li></ol><p>Crafted from renewable resources, our&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;help reduce reliance on single-use plastics, contributing to a cleaner planet. Manufactured using sustainable practices, ensuring minimal environmental footprint throughout the production process.</p><ol><li><strong>Robust and Reliable Construction</strong></li></ol><p>Engineered with high-quality paper materials, our&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;are designed to withstand the rigors of everyday use, offering exceptional strength and durability. Reinforced handles provide added support, making these&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;ideal for carrying groceries, merchandise, or personal belongings with ease.</p><ol><li><strong>Versatile Usage for Various Applications</strong></li></ol><p>From retail shopping to event giveaways, these versatile&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;are suitable for a wide range of purposes, catering to both business and personal needs. Perfect for packaging goods, organizing items, or presenting gifts in an eco-friendly and stylish manner.</p><ol><li><strong>Customizable Options for Branding</strong></li></ol><p>Elevate your brand presence with custom printing or branding options available for our&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>. Personalize each bag with your logo, slogan, or artwork to enhance brand recognition and create a lasting impression on customers.</p><ol><li><strong>Biodegradable and Recyclable</strong></li></ol><p>After use, our&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;can be easily recycled or composted, minimizing waste and promoting a circular economy. Biodegradable materials ensure that even if disposed of improperly, these&nbsp;<strong>paper bags</strong>&nbsp;will naturally break down over time, leaving no harmful residue behind.</p>', '1745257707_3157_600 x 600 (D).jpg', '', '', 'Deli Paper Premium Paper Bags are a Step Above the Rest', 'Deli Paper offers eco-friendly paper bags that are perfect for any occasion. Ideal for food packaging, shopping and more, these bags are durable', '', 'active', '2025-04-21 16:50:54', '2025-05-07 05:23:32', 'yes'),
(6, 'Parchment Paper', 'parchment-paper', 'Try Deli Paper parchment paper in your baking and cooking to become a must-have item in British households. Designed for the home cook, our paper provides ease and effectiveness for every kitchen accomplishment.', '<p><strong>Non-Stick Surface:</strong></p><p>Try baking made easier by using our amazing non-stick parchment paper. No more lip smearing and stained cookie or cake tumblersthe final cookies and cakes slide off easily.</p><p><strong>Heat Resistant:</strong></p><p>Resists heat up to 220C (428F), making it perfect for all your baking, roasting, and cooking requirements.</p><p><strong>Easy Clean-Up:</strong></p><p>Experience easy and efficient cleanup. Use parchment paper on baking trays and roasting tins to avoid sticking, and cut down on washing up.</p><p><strong>Versatile Use:</strong></p><p>Not only great for baking, but also for roasting vegetables, wrapping fish to keep it juicy, and perfect for gifting.</p><p><strong>Eco-Friendly and Reusable:</strong></p><p>Our high-quality parchment paper can be wiped clean and reused, making it cost-effective and environmentally friendly.</p><p><strong>Why is Deli Papers Parchment Paper the Best?</strong></p><p>At Deli Paper, we strive to provide British kitchens, especially busy ones, with the best gear. All of our parchment paper is made from food-safe materials to ensure excellent performance. Whether youre a serious baker creating delicate cookies, a home cook roasting vegetables, or someone who values presentation in food gifts, Deli Papers parchment paper is a must-have tool.</p><p>Turn every cooking and baking task into a fun experience with Deli Papers parchment paper, available in rolls and convenient pre-cut sheets.</p><p><strong>Add a roll to your cart today and discover why Deli Paper parchment paper is an essential in every UK kitchen.</strong></p>', '1745257707_3417_600 x 600 (B).jpg', '', '', 'Deli Paper Premium Parchment Paper is Versatile.', 'Deli Paper parchment paper is available in a variety of uses. Ideal for baking, food wrapping, and cooking. Visit us for eco-friendly and practical kitchens.', '', 'active', '2025-04-21 16:51:02', '2025-05-07 05:23:48', 'yes'),
(7, 'Greaseproof Paper', 'greaseproof-paper', 'Discover a world where your food creations are enjoyed with elegance and efficiency, due to Deli Papers finest greaseproof paper. Crafted with care for the skilled British cook, this important kitchen companion transforms everyday tasks into wonderful experiences.', '<p><strong>Exquisite Non-stick Surface</strong></p><p>Enjoy hassle-free baking with our exceptional nonstick greaseproof paper. Perfect for delicate pastries, biscuits, and other baked treats, this paper ensures easy release, preserving the beauty of your creations.</p><p><strong>High Heat Resistance</strong></p><p>Deli Papers greaseproof paper is highly heat-resistant, making it ideal for baking, roasting, and more. Its durability means it performs well under high temperatures, providing reliable support for all your cooking needs.</p><p><strong>Moisture Barrier Quality</strong></p><p>Wrap your food in our moisture-resistant greaseproof paper to keep it fresh and flavorful. This quality makes it ideal for sandwiches, deli products, and as a substitute for parchment or baking paper.</p><p><strong>Elegance and Durability</strong></p><p>Our greaseproof paper adds an elegant touch to gift wrapping and creative projects. Its suitable for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://delipaper.co.uk/food-wrapping-paper/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 51, 102); background-color: transparent;\"><strong>personalized wrapping paper</strong></a>, brown paper bags, gift bags, and even butcher paper projects, providing durability with style.</p><p><strong>Environmentally Conscious and Reusable</strong></p><p>Crafted from eco-friendly, high-quality materials, our greaseproof paper is reusable, making it a sustainable and cost-effective choice for kitchen and gift-wrapping needs.</p><p><strong>Why Deli Papers Greaseproof Paper Stands Out</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://delipaper.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 51, 102); background-color: transparent;\"><strong>Deli Paper</strong></a>&nbsp;understands the demands of the modern British kitchen, offering greaseproof paper that is both practical and versatile. Its designed to provide flawless results, whether youre baking, roasting, or wrapping food. Beyond the kitchen, its elegant appearance and grease-resistant properties make it perfect for personalized gift wrapping, paper rolls, and creative projects.</p><p>Explore the quality and versatility of Deli Papers greaseproof paper, available in handy rolls and sheets that fit effortlessly into your kitchen and gift-giving routines. Add a roll to your cart today to experience why Deli Papers greaseproof paper is an essential for every UK home.</p>', '1745257707_3417_600 x 600 (B).jpg', '1745740714_9661_Premium Branded Greasproof Paper (800 x 600).jpg', '1745740813_6447_Sample_Show_Case_(600_x_600).jpg', 'Deli Paper Greaseproof Paper-Discover its Excellence', 'Greaseproof Paper from Deli Paper is more versatile than a simple kitchen tool. It enhances the cooking and baking process.\r\n', '', 'active', '2025-05-05 18:17:24', '2025-05-10 03:39:19', 'yes');

